What this diagram shows (simple words)
✔ Producer → topic → partition

Producer message bhejta hai → Kafka usse topic ke ek partition me daalta hai.

✔ Partition ke andar hi OFFSET hota hai

Offset = message ordering
Offset 0 → pehla message
Offset 1 → dusra message

✔ Brokers topic ke partitions store karte hain

Broker 1 → Partition-0, Partition-1

Broker 2 → Partition-2

Broker 3 → Replicas

✔ Consumer ALWAYS offset order me message read karta hai

0 → 1 → 2 → 3 (strict order)



