# ✅ **2. CONSUMER CODE (Order me messages padhta hai)**

```java
@KafkaListener(topics = "orders", groupId = "order-group")
public void consume(String message) {
    System.out.println("Consumed: " + message);
}
```

### 🔥 Explanation

Consumer hamesha **offset ke order me** read karta hai:

```
Order Created
Payment Done
Order Packed
Order Shipped
```

